This highly functional office warehouse is situated within the award winning Logis Estate, Just moments from the Greens Road / East Link interchange. 

The current occupier has been in occupation since Jan 2017 and has experienced significant business growth, so they’ll be expanding to a new premises later this year. 

Key property features include:
-	Clear span warehouse of 1,116sqm*
-	Dual level office of 265sqm* including a welcoming reception area.
-	Secure yard with excellent container access
-	High clearance warehouse with good cubic capacity
-	21 on-site car spaces 
-	3-phase power 
-	Toilet / shower / lunch room amenities
-	Flexible lease terms available 

Enquire within for building plans and inspection times:

Lachlan Ferguson – 0448 082 112 – lachlan.ferguson@cbre.com.au

Ned Murphy – 0433 750 166 – ned.murphy@cbre.com.au

29 Babbage Drive, Dandenong South

Located moments from the Eastlink's Cheltenham Road on/off ramp, this office warehouse is easily accessible.

Perfect for small businesses, first time investors or additional storage space.

- Reception plus two management offices 45sqm*
- Warehouse storage 60sqm*

- 2 car parks on title.
- No automotive businesses permitted.
- Roller door access
